I am marking EVERY Elite quest and dungeons as optional in this guide. Especially on release you should do them!!! You'll easily find groups for elite quests and dungeons.
Buy a Nethergarde Bitter and put it somewhere where you WILL NOT sell it, you will need it roughly at the end of lvl 60.
Text: Buy a Nethergarde Bitter and put it somewhere where you WILL NOT sell it, you will need it roughly at the end of lvl 60.

Name: Set your [H] to Hellfire Peninsula at [G54.2, 63.6Hellfire Peninsula]
Take the gryphon(at Wing commanderDabir'ee) and bombard the 2 Big Portals with the bombs in your inventory
Text: Take the gryphon(at Wing commanderDabir'ee) and bombard the 2 Big Portals with the bombs in your inventory

Name: Take the gryphon(at Wing commanderDabir'ee) to fly to Shattered Point
Text: Take the gryphon(at Wing commanderDabir'ee) to fly to Shattered Point

Name: Take the gryphon(at Gryphoneer Windbellow) to the Abyssal Shelf and bomb every demon you see with the bomb in your inventory. Focus on the Cannons and the big Demons
Text: Take the gryphon(at Gryphoneer Windbellow) to the Abyssal Shelf and bomb every demon you see with the bomb in your inventory. Focus on the Cannons and the big Demons

Name: Take the gryphon(at Gryphoneer Windbellow) to Honor point. DONT DO THE QUEST FROM HER!
Text: Take the gryphon(at Gryphoneer Windbellow) to Honor point. DONT DO THE QUEST FROM HER!

Name: You got a quest item called "Burning Legion Missive". Accept it.
